%%Creator: (ImageMagick)
%%Title: (Libro-img066.eps)
%%CreationDate: (2020-03-28T12:00:17+01:00)
%%BoundingBox: -0 -0 1101 532
%%HiResBoundingBox: 0 0 1101 532
